## Key Improvements Summary

| Aspect | Original | Refactored |
|--------|----------|------------|
| **Resource Management** | Manual `fopen`/`fclose` | RAII `ProcessHandle`, automatic cleanup |
| **Security** | Command injection vulnerable | Path validation, proper quoting, traversal detection |
| **Error Handling** | Silent failures, no validation | `std::expected`, comprehensive error codes |
| **Concurrency** | Not thread-safe | `std::atomic`, thread-safe design |
| **Windows API** | Deprecated `WinExec` | Modern `CreateProcess` with security attributes |
| **Logging** | No logging | spdlog integration, optional file logging |
| **Configuration** | Hardcoded path | `ConversionConfig` struct, fully configurable |
| **UI/UX** | Modal only | Configurable UI, async support, progress monitoring |
| **Testing** | Not testable | Dependency injection, testable static functions |
| **Path Handling** | String concatenation | `std::filesystem`, proper validation |
| **Process Monitoring** | Fire-and-forget | Exit code, timeout, cancellation, output capture |
| **Result Tracking** | No details | `ConversionResult` with full diagnostics |

